{"word":"ἄξων","slug":"ἄξων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄξων</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄγω'><el>ἄγω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>an axle</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>axis</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>οἱ ἄξονες</el>, <i>the wooden tablets of</i> Solon's <i>laws, made to turn upon an axis</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}